cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG

The paper proposes a technique for single image dehazing, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of regularization techniques, which falls under the category of cs.GR (Graphics). The paper mentions the use of deep learning-based methods, which falls under the category of cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also involves the use of interpolation techniques, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper mentions the use of Nearest-Neighbor-based techniques, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning).
